    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/2cf77834f6bdd761d33be38299c2c0ac.avif?t=1683878755\" width=554 height=96 /></span><br><i>酒店外人声熙攘，车灯骤然变亮，沉重的撞击声贯穿耳膜，伴随着缓缓流淌的鲜血，埋藏<br>多年的阴谋正式拉开帷幕……</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/caf4a862607e40f28f347f57fec8f6c1.poster.avif?t=1683878755\" width=422 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/caf4a862607e40f28f347f57fec8f6c1.webm?t=1683878755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/caf4a862607e40f28f347f57fec8f6c1.mp4?t=1683878755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你本是荣归故里的退役兵王，却在回家当天目睹至亲遭遇离奇车祸。<br>一步步剥丝抽茧，追查线索，探寻老宅深处隐匿的密室，卧底成为许氏集团千金的贴身保镖，<br>邂逅家道中落的当红一线明星，与敌友难分的神秘人暗中交锋...…<br>斡旋于各方势力之间，调查他们的过往与秘密。 <br>谋杀之案，密室之谜。<br>她究竟是谁？<br>这一切与那场尘封已久的旧案又有什么关系？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/10781bf1fe2b8a88c0052ff70c1c6389.poster.avif?t=1683878755\" width=422 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/10781bf1fe2b8a88c0052ff70c1c6389.webm?t=1683878755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/10781bf1fe2b8a88c0052ff70c1c6389.mp4?t=1683878755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>深入迷局，逆光而行，是放任欲望在阴影下缓慢膨胀 ，还是拨开重重迷雾，偏向虎山行。 <br>阴谋与复仇 ，信任与背叛 ，情义与道义 。<br>一念跌入黑暗，一念走向光明。<br>结局如何，由你来书写！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/d9ab71c1c34c2d034293bc8a11dcea10.poster.avif?t=1683878755\" width=422 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/d9ab71c1c34c2d034293bc8a11dcea10.webm?t=1683878755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/d9ab71c1c34c2d034293bc8a11dcea10.mp4?t=1683878755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>▪ 多分支剧情走向，未知的结局引向何方</strong><br>四大女主支线 ，玩家自由定制剧本走向，在跌宕起伏的案件中探索人性的更多可能，你的<br>每一次抉择，都至关重要！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/bfc11ad5dc87013ffd5e4e6acf920727.poster.avif?t=1683878755\" width=422 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/bfc11ad5dc87013ffd5e4e6acf920727.webm?t=1683878755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/bfc11ad5dc87013ffd5e4e6acf920727.mp4?t=1683878755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>▪ 多重互动玩法，是时候表演真正的技术了</strong><br>紧张刺激的QTE操作，深度代入的拟真交互，有趣烧脑的VR全景式搜证解谜 ，让你身临其境<br>感受主角面临的危机。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/7139bd9e988e8a30adbb039f70b60016.poster.avif?t=1683878755\" width=422 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/7139bd9e988e8a30adbb039f70b60016.webm?t=1683878755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251020/extras/7139bd9e988e8a30adbb039f70b60016.mp4?t=1683878755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>▪真实线索墙 ，思考是破局的关键</strong><br>精心打造推理过程的每一步细节，帮你从蛛丝马迹中追寻线索，与主角一起揪出幕后真凶。<br><br><strong>▪《逆光》剧组原班人马，全视频真人实拍演绎</strong><br>改编自高甜与悬疑并存的《为你逆光而来》 ，剧版专业影视团队，原班人马再度演绎，<br>打造声与影的沉浸式体验；原创全新剧情走向，这一次他们的命运，由你来书写！",
